				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 08 Oct 2020 02:43:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>fastandbulbous</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2139686</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I do appreciate learning more about Hennessy, since I’ve enjoyed reading about him in the On Mount Alagadda canon. However, the anomaly in this article struck me as “another object that transports you to a spooky place (often a farmhouse)”, which I feel is pretty played out (and which I’m also guilty of with 2127). The exploration didn’t add enough to it to really draw me in. The writing is quality, but -1 from me</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13794173#post-4790559</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13794173/scp-4614#post-4790559</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2020 06:57:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This was really surprising, I thought I knew what I was getting into when the article started but it took a left turn prettt quickly. Also wanna commend you on the tension present throughout the log, genuinely made me feel uncomfortable despite no monsters or body horror&#8230; just this sense of unease building to a crescendo (sorry for the music analogy, no pun intended)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
