						 <p>I wanted to take a moment to go back and imagine what Hennessy might have lost his hearing to. I figured being in an audio based MTF unit must have exposed him to something, so this is that.</p> <p>This is also an entry for my team in the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/canon-renaissance-contest">Canon Renaissance Contest</a>. If you haven't yet, you should check one of the other entries. Might I suggest <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/gagliarda-part-one">this one</a>?</p> <hr /> <p><strong>Valued Critters:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602068765" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5903100&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602068765" alt="Pedagon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5903100)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" >Pedagon</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6091992&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602068765" alt="Sonderance" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6091992)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" >Sonderance</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yellowislol" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6284593&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602068765" alt="YellowISlol" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=